          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1661250652489-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>parsley </strong>and<strong> dill</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>smoked basa fillet[s] </strong>into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
